WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.610 --> 00:00:06.710
How to Give Tours on Club Penguin.

00:00:06.710 --> 00:00:11.139
If you're an experienced Club Penguin player,
giving guided tours is a great way to help

00:00:11.139 --> 00:00:12.790
out other people's penguins.

00:00:12.790 --> 00:00:23.290
You will need Club Penguin membership 45 days
of age Quiz answers Tour guide hat and penguins

00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:24.520
to guide.

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:26.270
Step 1.

00:00:26.270 --> 00:00:29.050
Achieve at least 45 days.

00:00:29.050 --> 00:00:34.210
Your penguin must be at least 45 days old
in order to be eligible for tour guide status.

00:00:34.210 --> 00:00:35.540
Step 2.

00:00:35.540 --> 00:00:39.160
Navigate your penguin to Ski Village and then
click on the Tour Guide booth.

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:44.690
When you're a tour guide, you can give one
penguin a tour or wait for a whole group.

00:00:44.690 --> 00:00:46.020
Step 3.

00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:49.850
Take the quiz you are given after clicking
on the Tours booth.

00:00:49.850 --> 00:00:56.420
The answer to the question "How does the pink
puffle play?" is "Skips with skipping rope."

00:00:56.420 --> 00:01:02.820
The answer to the question "What is the name
of the big fish in ice fishing?" is "Mullet."

00:01:02.820 --> 00:01:06.360
You will be asked eight of 15 possible questions.

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:07.650
Step 4.

00:01:07.650 --> 00:01:09.280
Continue the quiz.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:14.040
The answer to the question "What day does
the newspaper come out?" is "Thursday."

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:19.530
The answer to "Which of these games has a
shark in it?" is "Jet pack adventure."

00:01:19.530 --> 00:01:25.330
Answer the question "What color of puffle
can catch on fire?" by entering "Black."

00:01:25.330 --> 00:01:27.300
Step 5.

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:32.131
Answer the question "How many coins does it
cost to buy a player card background?" by

00:01:32.131 --> 00:01:34.150
saying "60."

00:01:34.150 --> 00:01:39.500
Complete the question "What is thrown out
of the truck in level 4 of bean counters?"

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:41.979
with the answer "Flowerpot."

00:01:41.979 --> 00:01:48.350
The answer to "In what room can you find old
copies of the Penguin Times?" is "Boiler room."

00:01:48.350 --> 00:01:50.170
Step 6.

00:01:50.170 --> 00:01:55.710
Answer "What is the name of Captain Rockhopper's
ship?" with "The Migrator," and answer "Which

00:01:55.710 --> 00:02:00.530
of these rooms does not have a game in it?"
with the option "Beach."

00:02:00.530 --> 00:02:03.340
If asked "Which room has a cuckoo clock?"

00:02:03.340 --> 00:02:08.200
answer "Ski Lodge," and "How do you get a
pin?" with "Click on it."

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:13.580
Finally, if asked "Which of these places doesn't
have music playing in the background?"

00:02:13.580 --> 00:02:15.170
answer "Pet Shop."

00:02:15.170 --> 00:02:16.810
Step 7.

00:02:16.810 --> 00:02:20.690
Answer seven of the eight questions you're
asked on the quiz, and you'll receive your

00:02:20.690 --> 00:02:22.390
tour guide hat.

00:02:22.390 --> 00:02:25.790
You can put the hat on if you're not wearing
anything else.

00:02:25.790 --> 00:02:30.230
You'll be given a sign that says "Tours Here"
if you wave.

00:02:30.230 --> 00:02:32.980
Wave by pushing the W key on the keyboard.

00:02:32.980 --> 00:02:34.700
Step 8.

00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:39.410
Click on the Tours booth again and read the
guide to help you be a good tour guide and

00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:42.760
help other people's penguins along their way.

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:48.230
Did you know Most penguins can swim about
15 miles per hour.

